"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"本质上，我们都是预言家，买股票，看的是未来一段时间涨价，你预期它会涨；做投机，你做多，你预言未来几分钟甚至几个小时股票会涨，做空，预言未来会跌。投资或者投资的真正可怕之处，就是一旦你预计错误，你将会拿着你的真金白银去实践，如果说好听一些，你是去投资，如果说不好听，就是去睹，其实我们从生下来的那一刻开始，就在开始赌博，只是你没有发现而已。\\n\\n> ### 众生平等，我们都是赌徒\\n\\nBuying stock in Amazon or pPet.com in 2000 was a bet on how the next decade would look, Getting married can be a bet on how you’ll feel about someone over the next half-century.It’s a big deal,right?\\n\\n当然，如果你有预言未来的能力，这一切都不是赌，这就是你生活中很普通的片段而已。\\n\\n![Chinese God of Wealth](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/92mTab_qLCHq3PIsBVPCk.png?height=511&width=511)\\n\\n* A bubble is an objectively irrational shared belief in a potential future\\n* Buying stock it would have been partly a matter of luck.\\n* the two things that kill a company during a bubble are excessive optimism,and the unwillingness to be sufficiently optimistic.\\n\\n  > one way to mitigate this  is to build a business around maximizing future,rather than present,hype.\\n  >\\n  > At the peak of optimism,some companies will be tempted to announce vaporware,to bring investors closer and push competitors further away.\\n\\n  [crowdfund://undefined?features=overview,backers](crowdfund://undefined?features=overview,backers)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637570013,\"title\":\"众生平等，我们都是赌徒（测试）\"},\"digest\":\"74T1_mXwIx77kwly91N1K7MEsshKz9SqWh8xzLwZH-8\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x13DbAB74f49888B1EA5A71D17ae41D90a3A7003B\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"wTAHUrGovWFr7ZL97TddvPyB5xhcebjiRK2-D2kyg28\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"a24ZjvJPKyD_7rG2QVs_65ynXzC1DSIq1iNnR6Wcs1M\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"yd6DzcSkUQsKenAMsPEOYOLwX5dmB2k_WIB4WKlVUIJiiYzkcO0TxNtX8nNpmC7-iSemTDydcy-q1qeVGJLIdQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xdaf622be3f2ef62608b5e4e0967a2f2f54395c4f1c60633684952b6c54f34d8d4c82e5895a9ef79ffd16f4fac8a8dfd50882cb09597907cb9fc35bdba9d1412a1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mi